---
import CountdownCard from "./CountdownCard.astro";
import CountdownMap from "./CountdownMap.astro";
---

<section class="w-full py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32 lg:py-40 section-padding-x bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-400 to-blue-300 bg-[url('/images/elements/bgbatik.svg')] bg-top bg-repeat-y bg-[length:300px_40%] sm:bg-[length:400px_50%] md:bg-[length:600px_50%] lg:bg-cover relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-400/80 to-blue-300/80 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="container max-w-screen-xl mx-auto relative z-10 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:gap-8 md:gap-10 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-reikna text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-yellow-300 mb-3 sm:mb-4 leading-tight drop-shadow-lg">
          Langkah kecil hari ini, cerita besar menanti!
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs xs:text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-white drop-shadow leading-relaxed">
          Ribuan mahasiswa tahun ajaran, bersiaplah menyambut pengalaman luar biasa di Soedirman Student Summit 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <CountdownCard />
      <CountdownMap />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
